      <title>美银表示，货币市场显示出欧洲央行流动性流失的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/money-markets-show-impact-of-ecb-s-liquidity-drain-bofa-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行策略师表示，欧洲央行清理数万亿欧元过剩流动性的努力已经提高了该地区融资市场的借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-13/money-markets-show-impact-of-ecb-s-liquidity-drain-bofa-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Feb 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在重要的美国通胀报告发布之前股市回落：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在人们热切期待的通胀数据公布之前，美国股指期货在谨慎交易中下跌，该数据可能为美联储降息时机提供线索。美国国债和美元保持稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
